class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850310/extras/bbc1f9f05ece337e99fae9ce929f4c3e.avif?t=1742196154\" width=616 height=212 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850310/extras/b82db437a8bee448337272cc7f3b0908.avif?t=1742196154\" width=616 height=212 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850310/extras/d90e2fccfe14049368ba27884c69e0a9.avif?t=1742196154\" width=616 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· Voice Actor: Yui Horie, Mariko Kouda, Mayumi Iizuka, Akemi Sato, Yukari Tamura, Tomoko Kawakami, Ayako Kawasumi, Yuko Minaguchi, Maaya Sakamoto, Tomokazu Seki, Hiroshi Kamiya, Tomokazu Sugita</p>",
